{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436040692,"sessionID":"ses_316fcb99fffew5IdSvpvZvnqV0","part":{"id":"prt_ce90649f00015YGuGqWnXrF2YL","sessionID":"ses_316fcb99fffew5IdSvpvZvnqV0","messageID":"msg_ce906418a001jMqeSjDwAHMiLB","type":"text","text":"Everything is complete. Let me provide a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### What was built\n\n**`src/lib/format-converter.ts`** — A new module that converts agency-agents registry format to woco-compatible agent template format.\n\n### Format Differences Handled\n\n| Aspect | Agency-Agents Format | Woco Format |\n|--------|---------------------|-------------|\n| **Frontmatter** | `name`, `description`, `color`, `emoji`, `vibe` | `description`, `mode: primary` |\n| **Headers** | Emoji-prefixed (`## 🧠 Your Identity`) | Clean (`## Your Identity`) |\n| **Body structure** | Personality-driven sections | Operational sections |\n| **Mode field** | Not present | Required (`primary`) |\n\n### Key Components\n\n1. **`isAgencyAgentFormat(rawMd)`** — Heuristic detection based on frontmatter fields (`name` without `mode`, presence of `color`/`emoji`/`vibe`)\n\n2. **`parseAgencyAgent(rawMd)`** — Parses agency-agents markdown into structured form: frontmatter fields + categorized body sections (identity, core mission, critical rules, workflow, deliverables, etc.)\n\n3. **`convertAgencyToWoco(agent)`** — Maps agency-agents fields to woco format:\n   - Combines `description` + `vibe` into woco `description` frontmatter\n   - Adds `mode: primary`\n   - Preserves all specialized domain content\n   - Strips emoji prefixes from headers via `cleanEmojiHeaders()`\n\n4. **`normalizeAgentFormat(rawMd)`** — Convenience entry point: detects format, converts if agency-agents, passes through unchanged if already woco-compatible\n\n### Integration\n\nModified **`src/lib/templates.ts`** `patchImportedAgent()` to call `normalizeAgentFormat()` before any patching steps. This ensures agency-agents definitions are converted to woco-compatible format before the description patch, body start/end patches, portless injection, and placeholder substitution run.\n\n### Build Verification\n\n✅ TypeScript typecheck passes  \n✅ Build succeeds (0.95 MB bundle, 152 modules)","time":{"start":1773436040691,"end":1773436040691}}}
